 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EScalr is an open source Cloud Management tool that brings automation to web applications. \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EScalr is a sysadmin robot that monitors servers. When load increases, the robot adds server capacity. When load decreases, it powers down a few machines. Scalr takes backups and stores them on S3, and other utilities ranging from cron to raid volumes. Scalr is equipped with different features such as auto-scaling, high availability, fault tolerance, backups, multi-cloud deployments and hybrid cloud bursting.\u003C/p\u003E",
